2+1.sig_info: The Sorcerer Supreme automatically counters enemy Buff Effects with countermagic. Spell effectiveness: 15 to 80%!

PASSIVE: Doctor Stephen Strange invokes three Vishanti blessings to aid him in battle, each lasting 9 seconds.
Oshtur's Refuge grants increased Armor and Block Proficiency for 9 seconds.
Agamotto's Insight grants increased Attack and Critical Hit Rate for 9 seconds.
Hoggoth's Wisdom grants 16% Ability Power Rate, and all hits Regenerate 14.37 Health for 9 seconds.
Doctor Strange receives 100% less Power from Attacking and Defending, but gains 33% Power every 9 seconds.
SPECIAL ATTACK 1: This attack may deal up to 100% additional damage and recover up to 100% Power at random.
SPECIAL ATTACK 2: While under Oshtur's Refuge, these flames have a 50% chance to inflict Weakness, decreasing the target's Attack by 15% for 10 seconds.
While under Agamotto's Insight, these flames have a 50% chance to Armor Break, applying 685.71 Armor Rating reduction for 10 seconds.
While under Hoggoth's Wisdom, these flames have a 50% chance to Nullify, removing 1 positive status effect from the opponent.
SPECIAL ATTACK 3: 100% chance to Fate Seal the Opponent immediately Nullifying all Buffs, and prevents any new Buffs from activating for 5 seconds.
